item.description:
Fights is a constant back-and-forth between the Hearthbound Embers and their opponents, following a simple flow:
Players Regain <a data-href="ENERGY" href="ds-(during-stabbings)/playerside/energy.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">ENERGY</a> (N x 2) -&gt; Players coordinate their actions, and lay out their cards in order of play -&gt; The Cards take effect -&gt;
Alternatively, Players lay out their cards, which take effect when declared -&gt;
Players then draw cards (N x 3) before the enemies start their turn, giving time to coordinate -&gt;
Enemies act out their Intents, and show new ones. -&gt; REPEAT Enemies realise their signalled Intent -&gt; Players Draw (N x 3) fresh cards -&gt; The Enemies signal their Intents -&gt; REPEAT<br>
